<h2 id="mission-objectives">Mission Objectives</h2>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>King of the Hill: Control the objective at the end of the game to score 3 points. If the objective is contested, each player contesting the objective gains 1 point instead.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Linebreaker: Score 1 point if you have a unit fully within the opponents deployment zone. Score 2 points instead if you have three units fully within.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Slay the Warlord: Score 1 point if you slay an enemy warlord this game. Score 2 points instead if you slay three warlords.</p>
  </li>
</ul>
